## CognitoTokens.activatedAt property

> This API is provided as a beta preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Activation time represented as the number of milliseconds elapsed since 00:00:00 on January 1, 1970 in UTC.

**Signature:**

```typescript
activatedAt: number;
```
